token_info.name: Summer
token_info.description: Interactive audio/visual glitch instrument. Unmute the sound and then play it with the keyboard: Keys a-z: Play different parts of track; Key 1: short glitch; Key 2: Reverse; Key 3: Random Speed; Key 4: Original Speed; Key 5: Turn on sequence; Key 6: New Sequence; Key 7: Change seq. params; Key 8: Patterns of 5;
